Content of mysql-ha-utils:
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
mhadmin.cron	A sample (recommended) crontab
mhadmin		SHELL script for MySQL backup, restore and service actions
README		This file

Configuration instructions
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Store your global configuration parameters inside the ``mhadmin'' script.
If you need to specify some local options, place them into a local
configuration file. Theese options override the global ones. If you use
a local configuration file, specify a path to this file in the global
section of ``mhadmin''.

Installation instructions
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1) Place ``mhadmin'' script into a directory containing binaries, e.g.
   /root/bin/.
2) Run ``mhadmin'' by typing mhadmin or ./mhadmin.
3) If some dependencies are missing, the script stops and announces them.

Operating instructions
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
See output of ``mhadmin''.

